em</strong> of all time with more than 35% of websites powered. </p>\n<p>And the common reason is that of its simple panel with extraordinary plugins that can serve smallest to giant services you want on your website, <strong>WITHOUT CODING</strong>! </p>\n<p>Plugins are the hardcore strength of WordPress and there are more than <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">55k various plugins</a> and it is hard (obviously) to find out the best one that can help you out blogging. </p>\n<p><strong>So, here we are with the best blogging tools and Plugins for WordPress that will assist you to grow with full throttle.</strong></p>\n<h4>1. Blog Designer</h4>\n<p>This plugin has been a game changer, especially for bloggers. Blog Designer WordPress plugin (Freemium) offers you to change and exhibit your page with many different layouts and templates. There are many various kinds of layouts for diverse use of it. Must have plugin to make your posts or web page looks cool.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Blog-Designer.png\" alt=\"Blog Designer\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4754\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/blog-designer/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Akismet</h4>\n<p>Akismet (Free) checks all the comments and contact form submissions for spam and malware through its global database and prevents your site from publishing threat and malicious content. User has the option to review the comment Spam that is spotted by akismet in Comment section. It is very essential plugin for all the bloggers out there.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Akismet-Anti-Spam.jpg\" alt=\"Akismet Anti-Spam\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4757\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/akismet/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. Yoast SEO</h4>\n<p>Yoast SEO (Freemium) is by far the best SEO plugin WordPress ever had. A standout and the most famous approaches to get movement to your blog posts, especially when you don&#8217;t have an established audience, is through Search Engine Optimization (SEO). Organic search traffic originates from people who use Google, Bing or other search engines from looking into particular phrases. And, Yoast SEO will be your best friend in generating step-to-step SEO for each page, post and your whole website.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Yoast-SEO.png\" alt=\"Yoast SEO\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4758\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>4. MailChimp</h4>\n<p>Bloggers&#8217; important tips also include to have a mailing list to directly call the and get the returning audience. Personally, Mailchimp (Freemium) will get you the perfect newsletter layout and also gives limited free mailing list. Highly recommended for start-up bloggers.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/MailChimp.png\" alt=\"MailChimp\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4760\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-wp/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Trash Duplicate and 301 Redirect</h4>\n<p>Duplication of content should be strictly deserted for the sake of good SEO of your website. Trash Duplicate and 301 Redirect WordPress plugin (Freemium) fetches the duplicate content from your website and grants you to remove it. Also, it offers the option to redirect to another URL from the post URL that you delete. This plugin is really helpful and can solve many problems.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Trash-Duplicate-and-301-Redirect.png\" alt=\"Trash Duplicate and 301 Redirect\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4761\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/trash-duplicate-and-301-redirect/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>6. User Activity Log</h4>\n<p>This plugin is beneficial if you have a team and you need to keep an eye on everyone&#8217;s work. User Activity log (Freemium) is a free WordPress plugin that helps admin to monitor all the activity of other admins and users of your sites&#8217; admin panel. The plugin tracks each and every detail of user from the moment one login.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/User-Activity-Log.png\" alt=\"User Activity Log\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4762\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/user-activity-log/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>7. Jetpack</h4>\n<p>Jetpack (Freemium) is one of the most essential and popular plugins in WordPress. It offers many functionality such as Stats and analytics, social media channel auto-share, and various different other security and backup services.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Jetpack.jpg\" alt=\"Jetpack\" width=\"903\" height=\"293\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4763\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>8. User Blocker</h4>\n<p>User Blocker WordPress plugin (Freemium) provides a facility to block any of the user accounts quickly with the defined time period. Gives more control on the admin panel and upon users of your website.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/User-Blocker.png\" alt=\"User Blocker\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4764\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/user-blocker/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>9. Avartan Slider</h4>\n<p>Sliders are essential to exhibit your website and highlight the best stuff that you have at the very front. Avartan Slider (Freemium) will do it for you at an utmost ease. Avartan slider plugin supports images, mp4 videos as well as Youtube and Vimeo videos so that you can add it up, and is fully responsive and optimized for all browsers and devices.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Avartan-slider.png\" alt=\"Avartan slider\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4765\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/avartan-slider-lite/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>10. Google Analytics</h4>\n<p>Most essential and much-needed plugin. Google Analytics (Free) is the best way to know the stats and core insights of your website that will help you to search for areas of improvements. It also helps from do your followers are coming, till when they are on your website and what they did during their stay. Google analytics is a must have a plugin for every small to big businesses.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Google-Analytics.jpg\" alt=\"Google Analytics\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4766\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/googleanalytics/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>11. Google Adwords Keyword Planner</h4>\n<p>If you are going low on the organic traffic from Google and other Search engines, this plugin can help you a lot. Keyword Planner (Free) can help devastatingly to plan out the interest area of your business and their most relatable keywords that have the capability to drive traffic to your website. Essential for SEO person and also for your website&#8217;s SEO to drive it to the right path.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Google-Adwords-Keyword-Planner-e1511939313385.png\" alt=\"Google Adwords Keyword Planner\" width=\"1024\" height=\"399\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4767\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://adwords.google.com/intl/en_in/home/tools/keyword-planner/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>12. Google Webmaster tools</h4>\n<p>Similar to Analytics, you can utilize these tools to track your site&#8217;s performance and recognize any issues. Webmaster tools (Free) additionally records traffic information and keywords, and you can likewise use these to advise search engines if you&#8217;ve made any reports on your webpage.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Google-Webmaster-tools.jpeg\" alt=\"Google Webmaster tools\" width=\"900\" height=\"446\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4768\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>13. Google Adsense</h4>\n<p>Now that we have talked about setting up your website absolutely, Google Adsense (Free) is the tool and plugin (available now) to monetize your website and earn money from your blog. Its bit easy to setup Adsense account and place in on your website.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Google-Adsense.png\" alt=\"Google Adsense\" width=\"604\" height=\"272\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4769\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/adsense/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>14. Popups</h4>\n<p>An excellent tool for popups (Freemium). Fully customizable plugin and can be used in many ways on many pages.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Ninja-Popups.jpg\" alt=\"Ninja Popups\" width=\"716\" height=\"336\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4770\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popups/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>15. Shareoholic</h4>\n<p>Let your users share your content and make you reach to many other visitors. Shareoholic (Freemium) gives you social share buttons above and below the post.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://avartanslider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Shareaholic.jpg\" alt=\"Shareaholic\" width=\"938\" height=\"304\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4771\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shareaholic/\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png\" alt=\"More Details\" width=\"155\" height=\"43\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-40898\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details.png 155w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/More-Details-150x43.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 155px) 100vw, 155px\" /></a></p>\n<p>So, these are the top 15 best blogging plugins for WordPress that will glamorize your blog and gives more power to you. If you know any other tools that could be benefited to WordPress blog site that do write it in the comment box below.</p>\n<p>Happy blogging!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/best-blog-wordpress-plugins/\">15 Best Blogging Plugins for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/best-blog-wordpress-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"Top 20 Digital Marketing Trends to Watch in 2018 and Beyond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"ht