:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:646:\"<p>It’s 2018 and the digital marketers are getting ready to face the disruptions and challenges coming in the way of achieving their goals. They bank on technological advancements time and again to address the client’s requirements and gain the optimum outcome. As we witness a transformation from a laptop and desktop-driven age into the mobile-driven </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/top-digital-marketing-trends/\">Top 20 Digital Marketing Trends to Watch in 2018 and Beyond</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21422:\"<p><strong>It’s 2018</strong> and the <strong>digital marketers are getting ready</strong> to face the disruptions and challenges coming in the way of achieving their goals. They bank on technological advancements time and again to address the client’s requirements and gain the optimum outcome. </p>\n<p>As we witness a transformation from a laptop and desktop-driven age into the mobile-driven era, the advent of new marketing trends is inevitable in the digital world. </p>\n<p><strong>Here we go through twenty noteworthy digital marketing trends that are going to impact the marketing strategy in the year 2018 and beyond:</strong> </p>\n<h3>1. AR will be game changer</h3>\n<p><strong>Pokémon Go</strong> has already shown what <strong>AR (Augmented Reality)</strong> integration with social media can do. As the number of smartphone users steadily increases across the world, different brands will tend to use AR to establish better engagement with consumers in the near future.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pokemon-go-giphy.gif\" alt=\"pokemon go\" width=\"480\" height=\"196\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40112\" /></p>\n<p><strong>For example,</strong> the AR technology will enable the brands to show content based on the customer’s location. Experts are of opinion that Instagram and FB will soon integrate AR into their platforms.</p>\n<h3>2. Importance of Influencers will Decrease</h3>\n<p>Companies spend a lot of bucks on influencers, but, they are <strong>unable to measure the results</strong> they could get. </p>\n<p>In the coming time, it is fairly possible that the influencer market will collapse as the <strong>brands move to organic promotional methods</strong> that are more affordable and effective than high-cost influencers. When it comes to increasing RoI, there is no alternative to traditional organic methods.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40116\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Importance-of-influencers-challenges-840x1024.png\" alt=\"Importance of influencers challenges\" width=\"520\" height=\"400\" class=\"size-large wp-image-40116\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Emarketer.com</p></div>\n<h3>3. Data will be Dominant</h3>\n<p>Data analysis has been mainstreamed in the year 2017, and now onward, we can see the <strong>rise of data-driven marketing</strong>. Marketers will make their strategies on the basis of clear understanding of consumer behavior and their overall journey from search to shopping. </p>\n<p>It is fair to mention that the digital marketing professionals will monitor the customer’s purchasing path from scratch to learn what compels them to buy.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40124\" style=\"width: 970px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Data-Driven-Marketing.jpg\" alt=\"Data Driven Marketing\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40124\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Teradata.com</p></div>\n<h3>4. Complete Mobile Takeover is Obvious</h3>\n<p>These days, handheld devices account for over 60 percent of all digital minutes worldwide. It includes Facebook advertising and searches. </p>\n<p><strong>In the year 2018 and beyond</strong>, we will witness a complete mobile takeover and digital marketing techniques will be based on the mobile platform. However, it does not mean that desktops and laptops will become obsolete, but yes, their charm will fade with time. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover.jpg\" alt=\"Mobile Takeover\" width=\"469\" height=\"359\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40130\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover.jpg 469w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover-300x230.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover-261x200.jpg 261w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover-327x250.jpg 327w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Mobile-Takeover-450x344.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></p>\n<h3>5. Micro-moments will remain in focus</h3>\n<p>Customers use their mobile devices for almost everything ranging from searching to purchasing. </p>\n<p><strong>In 2018</strong>, we certainly expect that more people will make instant decisions with the help of smartphones, which will lead to the rise of micro-moments. An integrated marketing strategy should be woven around these micro-moments to ensure that the brands show real-time information to potential customers whenever they look for information or advice.</p>\n<p><strong>Google</strong> calls these moments Micro-Moments. They’re the <strong>I want to know, I want to go, I want to do,</strong> and <strong>I want to buy moments</strong> that are loaded with intent, context, and immediacy. And the marketers have to be ready for it.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40136\" style=\"width: 1011px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/micro-moments.png\" alt=\"micro moments\" width=\"800\" height=\"311\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40136\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Thinkwithgoogle.com</p></div>\n<h3>6. Ads will be more purposeful</h3>\n<p>In any digital marketing campaign, ads play a vital role to reach a targeted audience. But then, people have already started giving less attention to the ads, marketers need to rebuild the ad strategy in 2018. </p>\n<p>Only purposeful ads with a highly specific objective and capacity to attract a targeted audience will work wonders. With this, we can also expect that mobile ad platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Snapchat will post a major growth in coming years.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40251\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Top-Social-Platforms-1024x939.png\" alt=\"Top Social Platforms\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" class=\"size-large wp-image-40251\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Wearesocial.com</p></div>\n<h3>7. Video would not enough</h3>\n<p>Though around 79 percent customers prefer to watch a video to know more about the product, the simple product video would not enough for 2018. Professional live videos will replace the product video and we will witness the active participation of social media platforms in showing them.</p>\n<p>The live video provides a great way to connect with the audience, and the customers like it more as compared to the simple video.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/facebook-live-1024x766.jpg\" alt=\"facebook live\" width=\"700\" height=\"350\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-40254\" /></p>\n<h3>8. Privacy will hold the key to success</h3>\n<p>Do you know that as per a <a href=\"https://home.kpmg.com/sg/en/home/media/press-releases/2016/11/companies-that-fail-to-see-privacy-as-a-business-priority-risk-crossing-the-creepy-line.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">KPMG survey</a>, almost 55 percent of consumers change their purchase decisions against some products due to privacy concerns?  </p>\n<p>In other words, commitment toward protecting the privacy of the consumers will benefit marketers in 2018 and beyond. It is, therefore, necessary to keep privacy protection in mind while making digital marketing strategies. </p>\n<h3>9. Conversational interfaces will become a norm</h3>\n<p>Voice and AR/VR interfaces or conversational interfaces are here to stay. Amazon’s Alexa, Google Assistant, Cortana, and chatbots will find their place in the consumer’s daily lives. Brands can interact naturally with the consumers&#8217; thanks to such interfaces. </p>\n<blockquote><p>65% of consumers feel good about themselves and the company when they can handle an issue without talking to a live person.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Chatbots facilitate the consumers to get the useful information or transaction assistance. Conversational interfaces will eventually bring the trend of voice marketing, which we will discuss later. </p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40260\" style=\"width: 640px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits.jpg\" alt=\"chatbots benefits\" width=\"630\" height=\"473\" class=\"size-full wp-image-40260\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits.jpg 630w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-300x225.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-500x375.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-624x468.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-266x200.jpg 266w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-333x250.jpg 333w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/chatbots-benefits-450x338.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Marketingoops.com</p></div>\n<h3>10. Personalized content is necessary</h3>\n<p>Every aspect of digital marketing is dependent on content in one or other way. Personalized content can attract and retain customers with ease, and lead them toward the purchase of products. Therefore, big brands will opt for personalized and unique content more than ever in 2018. We cannot rule out the possibility of the content-rich marketing campaigns combined with voice search, interactive tutorials, and featured snippets.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing.jpg\" alt=\"content marketing\" width=\"638\" height=\"479\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40264\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing.jpg 638w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-300x225.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-500x375.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-624x468.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-266x200.jpg 266w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-333x250.jpg 333w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/content-marketing-450x338.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px\" /></p>\n<h3>11. Inclusion of AI (Artificial Intelligence)</h3>\n<p>In a survey conducted by the Economist, almost 75 percent of business executives were of opinion that they will use AI actively in the business within next three years. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/AI-ChatBots.png\" alt=\"AI Chat Bots\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40326\" /></p>\n<p>How does AI help a digital marketing campaign? Well, chatbots and other interactive tools can give a real-time response to the customers’ queries and facilitate them to take a buying decision. Such tools can work on the basis of behavior analysis, and also, can relentlessly interact with multiple people at once.</p>\n<h3>12. IoT will increase RoI</h3>\n<p>The Internet of Things concept is replaced by the Internet of Everything. Yes, as per the <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.in/THE-INTERNET-OF-THINGS-2017-REPORT-How-the-IoT-is-improving-lives-to-transform-the-world/articleshow/58335244.cms\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Business Insider report</a>, businesses will spend <strong>$5 trillion</strong> on IoT solutions by 2021. </p>\n<p>Digital marketing experts need to utilize this concept for promoting products and services in an engaging way. As multiple connected ‘things’ remain close to the customers, it is easy for marketers to promote products using these things. </p>\n<p>Also, IoT devices are relatively more affordable as compared to other instruments, and they can increase RoI. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/IoT2020-e1524813871288-1024x710.jpeg\" alt=\"IoT 2020\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-40267\" /></p>\n<h3>13. Live Chat will gain ground</h3>\n<p>Do you know that customers want a business to be available 24/7? It is possible with technological advancements in AI and IoT technologies. </p>\n<p>Today, the real-time response matters the most in taking the purchasing decisions, and therefore, Live Chat is in limelight. It gives a feeling to the customers that the business is always ‘ON’ for them. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Live-Chat.png\" alt=\"Live Chat\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40275\" /></p>\n<h3>14. The Rise of Contextual Targeting Strategies</h3>\n<p>Let’s face it! Cookies have failed to track user behavior effectively. </p>\n<p>When <strong>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)</strong> will take place in May 2018, things will get more complicated for the ad tech vendors to use cookies for the same purpose. Therefore, we can certainly expect that contextual targeting strategies will replace cookies in 2018. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing.jpg\" alt=\"Contextual Targeting Strategies\" width=\"728\" height=\"546\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40306\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing.jpg 728w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-300x225.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-500x375.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-624x468.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-267x200.jpg 267w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-333x250.jpg 333w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/contextual-marketing-450x338.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\" /></p>\n<p>The rise of contextual targeting strategies will be largely attributed to the necessity for advertisers to understand the page context from the consumer viewpoint.</p>\n<h3>15. Localization is everywhere</h3>\n<p>In today’s mobile-driven era, localization plays a significant role in spreading brand awareness and boost the reputation of any business at the local level. </p>\n<p>Companies seeking to increase their market share through enhancing overall engagement can opt for a localization approach. The digital marketers also implement native advertising strategy to get the most of localization. Native ads in the language of local people can provide an opportunity for viral sharing and improved penetration on the target market.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_40310\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-1024x393.jpg\" alt=\"native advertising\" width=\"1024\" height=\"393\" class=\"size-large wp-image-40310\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-1024x393.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-300x115.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-768x295.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-500x192.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-624x240.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-850x326.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-350x134.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising-450x173.jpg 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/native-advertising.jpg 1401w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Moz.com</p></div>\n<h3>16. CX is a new trend</h3>\n<p>An ever-increasing competition in the digital world has compelled the marketers and entrepreneurs to focus on the <strong>Customer Experience (CX)</strong>. </p>\n<p>If any company aspires to embark on a digital transformation, CX will remain decisive in coming years. From transportation to education, and from retail to manufacturing, every industry sector needs to build and execute the CX strategy for improving customer experience.</p>\n<h3>17. Storytelling has a great future</h3>\n<p>No marketer would ignore the social media “stories” in the coming year. As the storytelling approach gains ground in social media networks, “stories” of Snapchat, Instagram Stories, and “Reels” from YouTube have started to become more powerful and prevalent than ever. </p>\n<p>It is also possible that WhatsApp and Facebook will also jump on the ‘Stories’ bandwagon. Stories can capture the best moments form a day and they stay for a fixed time.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-1024x498.png\" alt=\"stories evolution\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-40312\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-1024x498.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-300x146.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-768x374.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-500x243.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-624x304.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-850x414.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-350x170.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/stories-evolution-450x219.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>Their temporary stay is capable of creating a FOMO (Fear of Missing Out) feeling for users. Digital marketers can capitalize on stories to gain people’s attention.  </p>\n<h3>18. Real-life experiences will join the party</h3>\n<p>In the year 2018 and beyond, the real-life experiences will be considered while making digital marketing strategy.</p>\n<p><strong>For example,</strong> the online experience starts just before any sport or a mega event and lasts during the event. In the near future, marketers will also experiment the same and make their campaigns more consumer-centric. Such campaigns are more capable of attracting people toward any brand.</p>\n<h3>19. Voice marketing will increase</h3>\n<p>As per Google, 20 percent of mobile searches are based on voice, and the number will increase gradually as the consumers will get used to asking Alexa and Siri for useful information. </p>\n<p>The digital marketers need to concentrate on capturing voice searches and start giving ads on such platforms. In other words, voice marketing is all set to increase and the marketers must pay attention to it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Voice-Search_1.png\" alt=\"Voice Search \" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-40313\" /></p>\n<h3>20. Marketing transformation is visible</h3>\n<p>Marketing is in expansion mode through including most of the customer engagement processes on every available platform.</p>\n<p>The <strong>CMOs (Chief Marketing Officers)</strong> are busy in overhauling the process to make it more result-driven. Altogether, we can clearly see the transformation in marketing activities. There is no exaggeration in mentioning that the digital marketing will become smarter, more intelligent, and inclusive in the coming time.</p>\n<p><strong>Concluding lines:</strong><br />\n<strong>AI, IoT, AR,</strong> and other technologies are all set to bring radical changes in conventional digital marketing practices. Along with this, the user behavior and protection of their privacy will take center stage in the year 2018. It is interesting to see how digital marketers get adapted to these trends and come up with the strategies that address the marketing and branding requirements of their clients worldwide.</p>\n<p>At <strong>Solwin Infotech</strong>, our expert digital marketers are well-versed in using the cutting-edge automated tools. With a vast experience of serving the global clientele across various industry sectors, our professionals can come up with the most <strong>customized digital marketing campaign</strong> to get an optimum output. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\">Contact us</a> to know more about the customized digital marketing campaign for your business. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/top-digital-marketing-trends/\">Top 20 Digital Marketing Trends to Watch in 2018 and Beyond</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/top-digital-marketing-trends/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"Step-By-Step Guide To Web Design And Development Process\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";