:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35861:\"<p>Thinking to start an eCommerce store on Magento 2? Why settle with old instead of new?</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve something for you!! </p>\n<p>Kick off old version and arise your dream business with Magento 2.2.</p>\n<p>We have listed top 20 Magento 2.2 themes which all are compatible with latest web design trends. All the themes listed here are so powerful and customizable that can boost your sales easily. </p>\n<p>I swear that you will get confused or change your mind while scrolling for what kind of business you should start. All these themes are mostly multipurpose. So, you can use it for any eCommerce store.</p>\n<p>So, Let&#8217;s start scrolling.</p>\n<h3>1. FreeGo</h3>\n<p>FreeGo is more worthy than word called free. It is one of the best free Magento 2.2 themes with pro design. It has amazing features like off-canvas menu, featured &#038; new products list, user-friendly navigation, child theme ready,  and much more. It is a fully responsive theme for all kind of e-commerce stores.</p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo.png\" alt=\"FreeGo\" width=\"1583\" height=\"2540\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-38614\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-187x300.png 187w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-768x1232.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-638x1024.png 638w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-500x802.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-624x1001.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-850x1364.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FreeGo-125x200.png 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1583px) 100vw, 1583px\" /></p>\n<p>The theme includes <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/sold-out-label-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sold Out Label Magento 2 Extension</a> that helps you put a sold out label over the default image for all products which are out of stock. </p>\n<p>FreeGo nourishes store owner to make their business highly effective and improve revenue in the short run.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-themes/freego-responsive-theme-magento-2/\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>2. Shoptica</h3>\n<p>With responsive, eye-catching and straightforward design Shoptica covers all your needs for an Online shopping site. Shoptica gives great and smooth shopping experience. It refers to all kinds of marketplace businesses that needs a feature rich and beautiful presence Online. It can surcharge your megastores such as Fashion store, Cosmetics shop, Watch store, Digital store, Furniture store, Luxury jewelry and accessories.        </p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica.png\" alt=\"Shoptica\" width=\"1583\" height=\"1872\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38615\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-254x300.png 254w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-768x908.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-866x1024.png 866w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-500x591.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-624x738.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-850x1005.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Shoptica-169x200.png 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1583px) 100vw, 1583px\" /></p>\n<p>It comes with advanced mega menu feature which is a very powerful tool for creating a better look and professional navigation easily without technical knowledge. The theme includes  </p>\n<p>Shoptica leaves the impression of your store in customers mind that will encourage them to come again and again.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-themes/shoptica-ultimate-responsive-theme-magento-2/\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>3. Kosmic</h3>\n<p>Are you in confusion on which kind of business you wanna start or you wanna change your store type? Then Kosmic is suitable in both situations. This Magento 2 theme is built give boon for eCommerce, you can start any kinda business. Electronic gadget to handmade crafted products Kosmic will pull your sales ratio always upside.</p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic.png\" alt=\"Kosmic\" width=\"1583\" height=\"2169\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38616\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic-219x300.png 219w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic-768x1052.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic-747x1024.png 747w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic-500x685.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Kosmic-624x855.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcd