-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro.png\" alt=\"Pizzaro\" width=\"1583\" height=\"2524\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38552\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-188x300.png 188w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-768x1225.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-642x1024.png 642w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-500x797.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-624x995.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-850x1355.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Pizzaro-125x200.png 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1583px) 100vw, 1583px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/pizzaro-food-responsive-magento-1-2-theme/19438157?ref=solwin\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>17. Universal</h3>\n<p>Universal has 30 demos to run a powerful business website. You can find a variety of layouts for fashion, beauty, food and drinks, home goods, pets, games &#038; toys and electronics eCommerce store. One of the best parts is that you can customize store more natural way. Just click on an element which you want to customize and change its color, padding, font-size, etc.  </p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal.png\" alt=\"Universal\" width=\"1583\" height=\"1800\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38554\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-264x300.png 264w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-768x873.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-901x1024.png 901w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-500x569.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-624x710.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-850x967.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Universal-176x200.png 176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1583px) 100vw, 1583px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/universal-responsive-magento-theme/12335130?ref=solwin\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>18. Evolution Store</h3>\n<p>Evolution Store is simple and elegant Magento 2.2 theme for small business. It carries 12 amazing homepages, 6+ Ceramix Child Theme, 5+ Kitchen Child Theme, 4+ Cool stuff Child Theme. On the homepages you can show bestsellers, new arrival, featured, random, latest and special products. It makes everything easier than ever with the support of drag n drop page builder.</p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store.png\" alt=\"Evolution Store\" width=\"1455\" height=\"2497\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38559\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store.png 1455w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-175x300.png 175w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-768x1318.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-597x1024.png 597w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-500x858.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-624x1071.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-850x1459.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Evolution-Store-117x200.png 117w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1455px) 100vw, 1455px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/m2themes-evolution-magento-2-template/17547253?ref=solwin\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>19. SM Market</h3>\n<p>SM Market is an extremely powerful and flexible premium Magento theme with responsive &#038; retina ready design. This theme is the best choice for any types of store and comes with lots of awesome functions. It features powerful admin panel, one-click to import data, multiple listing layouts, countdown timer, etc are really worthy.</p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket.png\" alt=\"SM Smarket\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1964\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38560\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket.png 1456w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-222x300.png 222w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-768x1036.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-759x1024.png 759w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-500x674.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-624x842.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-850x1147.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/SM-Smarket-148x200.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1456px) 100vw, 1456px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/sm-smarket-fluid-responsive-magento-22-fashion-theme/21050102?ref=solwin\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<h3>20. Torano</h3>\n<p>Torano is a latest released theme for Magento 2.2. It has 5+ pixel perfect demos with amazing color combinations. Surely it&#8217;s fresh starting and design structure will blow your mind. It&#8217;s stunning hover effects, unlimited footer and header option, PSD included, cleverly layered navigation extension, social login newsletter popup, etc are the highlights.</p>\n<p><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano.png\" alt=\"Torano\" width=\"1460\" height=\"1949\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38562\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano.png 1460w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-225x300.png 225w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-768x1025.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-767x1024.png 767w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-500x667.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-624x833.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-850x1135.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Torano-150x200.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1460px) 100vw, 1460px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/torano-supermarket-marketplace-magento-2-theme/21200385?ref=solwin\"><img src=\'\' data-src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Details.png\" alt=\"Details\" width=\"165\" height=\"46\" class=\"lazyload aligncenter size-full wp-image-38513\" /></a></p>\n<p>